## Testing Standards

- Use `{{TEST_FRAMEWORK}}` for all tests
- Mock external services in unit tests — never hit real APIs
- Test pure logic functions against synthetic data

**Running tests:**
```bash
{{TEST_COMMAND}}              # full suite
